markdown
# 🇲🇾 Malaysian Trade Policy Scraper

Scrape Malaysian government trade websites. Then ask AI questions about the policies.

---

## 📂 Files

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `CustomsExportReader.py` | Main one - scrapes 5 websites, uses Gemini AI (ilmu.ai as backup) |
| `CustomsExportReader2.py` | Simple one - scrapes 1 website, Gemini only |
| `.env` | Put your API keys here |

---

## 🚀 How To Run

### 1. Install packages
```bash
pip install beautifulsoup4 requests python-dotenv google-genai
2. Put API keys in .env file
text
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_key_here
Z_AI_API_KEY=your_ilmu_key_here
3. Run
bash
python CustomsExportReader.py
4. Ask questions!
text
❓ You: What documents needed for K2 export form?
🤖 Expert: Based on Customs Export Procedure, you need...
⚠️ Problems?
Problem	Solution
Gemini 503 error	Wait 1-2 minutes, retry. Or use CustomsExportReader2.py
ModuleNotFoundError	Run pip install command above
Z_AI_API_KEY not found	Check your .env file exists
Some websites fail	Malaysian gov sites block bots. Can't fix.
🌐 Websites Scraped
Customs eZ-HS Portal (tariff codes)

MITI RCEP FTA (trade agreement)

Customs Export Procedure (how to export)

Federal Legislation (customs law)

WCO Harmonized System (HS codes)